Class CollaborationSingleRootApplication

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.irian.ankor.application.BaseApplication
      • at.irian.ankor.application.SimpleSingleRootApplication
        • at.irian.ankor.application.CollaborationSingleRootApplication
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Application
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnimalsServerApplication, TodoServerApplication

    public abstract class CollaborationSingleRootApplication
extends SimpleSingleRootApplication
    Convenient base class for Ankor applications that support model instance sharing (i.e. collaboration). Like SimpleSingleRootApplication this implementation supports an arbitrary number of model instances that all have the same model root name (typically called "root"). In addition to that a client may reconnect to an existing model instance by providing a "model instance id".
    See Also:
